Mia was a mite who loved money. She saved her money in a maroon piggy bank. She loved to make her money multiply. She made many dollars by selling muffins. She also saved her money for a magic show. May was the month when the show was on. Mia was thrilled! She bought more snacks and went to the show with her family. She enjoyed the magic show, and she was happy to have saved enough money to enjoy it.
